meico.mpm.elements.maps

Class GenericMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • meico.xml.AbstractXmlSubtree
      • meico.mpm.elements.maps.GenericMap
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArticulationMap, AsynchronyMap, DynamicsMap, ImprecisionMap, MetricalAccentuationMap, OrnamentationMap, RubatoMap, TempoMap

    public class GenericMap
extends AbstractXmlSubtree
    This class interfaces MPM maps on a more general level. It forms the basis for the more dedicated classes for specific maps.
    Author:
    Axel Berndt

      • updateAttributeValues

        public void updateAttributeValues(java.lang.String attributeName,
                                  java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> valueMappings)
        This method iterates through all elements of the map. If they have an attribute of the specified name, its value will be replaced according to the hashmap's mappings (current value -> new value). If the current value does not appear in the hashmap it is left unaltered.
        Parameters:

        valueMappings -
